```plantuml
@startuml xinsongyan_talos_pal_locomotion_slmc

actor User
participant "ROS Node" as ROS
participant "DCM Controller" as DCM
participant "WBC Plugin" as WBC
participant "State Estimator" as Estimator
participant "Safety Layer" as Safety
participant "TALOS Robot" as Robot

User -> ROS: Start locomotion command
activate ROS

ROS -> DCM: Generate walking pattern
activate DCM
DCM --> ROS: Reference trajectory
deactivate DCM

ROS -> Estimator: Request state estimate
activate Estimator
Estimator --> ROS: Pose/velocity data
deactivate Estimator

ROS -> Safety: Check safety conditions
activate Safety
Safety --> ROS: Safety status
deactivate Safety

alt Safe conditions met
    ROS -> WBC: Execute whole-body control
    activate WBC
    WBC -> Robot: Send joint commands
    activate Robot
    Robot --> WBC: Sensor feedback
    deactivate Robot
    WBC --> ROS: Control status
    deactivate WBC
else Unsafe conditions
    ROS -> Safety: Trigger safety protocol
    activate Safety
    Safety -> Robot: Emergency stop
    deactivate Safety
end

ROS --> User: Operation status
deactivate ROS

@enduml
```